      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs used in validation must directly correspond to the QoIs required for the COU decision. Gradation 2 required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Primary QoI is the relative hemolysis index (RH), which is the direct metric used in the COU acceptance criterion (RH < 1). Validation performed on the same QoI as the COU decision metric. Secondary QoIs including shear stress distribution and exposure time also validated, achieving Gradation 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
