      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published literature demonstrating superior performance in rotating blood-contacting devices. Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model used with modified coefficients from Heuser and Opitz. Model form selection justified by literature survey and sensitivity study comparing three turbulence model variants."
