      "rationale": "Blood viscosity, density, and hemolysis model coefficients identified as key inputs. Nominal values from published literature with documented sources. Sensitivity analysis performed for ±10% variation in hemolysis model coefficients, showing less than 15% variation in predicted RH, considered acceptable for comparative analysis."
